                     <summary><title type="supplied">Brot af kvæðum</title>
                        <note>Flestir efnisþættirnir virðast hafa tilheyrt sama handriti frá upphafi.</note></summary>
                        <textLang mainLang="is">Íslenska</textLang>
                        <msItem n="1" class="kvad" defective="true">
                            <title type="supplied">Brot af kvæðum.</title>
                            <note><p>Hér eru m.a. varðveitt kvæði eftir <name type="person" key="JonGud003">Jón Guðmundsson lærða.</name></p>
                                <p>Bl. <locus from="8" to="9">8-9</locus> sködduð að neðan.</p>
                                <p>Bl. <locus from="10v" to="10v">10v</locus> upprunalega autt.</p>
                            </note>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem n="2" class="kvad" defective="true">
                            <title type="supplied">Kvæðabrot.</title>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem n="3" class="kvad" defective="true">
                            <title type="supplied">Kvæðabrot.</title>
                            <note>Bl. <locus from="10v" to="11r">10v-11r</locus> auð.</note>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem n="4" class="kvad" defective="true">
                            <title type="supplied">Rímnabrot</title>
                            <note>
                                <p>Úr: <title type="uniform">Rímum af Víglundi og Ketilríð</title>, <title type="uniform">Rímum af Nikulási leikara</title>, <title type="uniform">Rímum af Hálfdani Brönufóstra</title> (Brönurímum gömlu), <title type="supplied">Kaupmannarímum</title>, <title type="supplied">Saknaðarrímu</title> og <title type="uniform">Rímum af Úlfi Uggasyni</title>.</p>
                                <p>Efri hlutinn á bl. <locus from="14" to="14">14</locus> rifinn burt.</p>
                                <p>Bl. <locus from="58" to="59">58-59</locus> eru geymd sér (sjá varðveislusögu).</p>
                            </note>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem n="5" class="salm" defective="true">
